 ATEEZ 宣布“走向光明：权力意志”世界巡演 2025 年欧洲站https://www.nme.com/news/music/ateez-2024-world-tour-towards-the-light-will-to-power-2-3555883?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ateez-2024-world-迈向光之意志之旅2Gladys Yeo Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:15:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3555796 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ateez 世界巡回演唱会 2024 2025 欧洲音乐会" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在伦敦、柏林、巴黎等地举办音乐会</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ateez-2024-world-tour-towards-the-light-will-to-power-2-3555883">ATEEZ 宣布“走向光明：权力意志”世界巡演 2025 年欧洲站的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ateez 世界巡回演唱会 2024 2025 欧洲音乐会" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ateez-2024-world-tour-081223-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont