r /><strong>03：荷兰阿姆斯特丹，Ziggo Dome</strong><br /> <strong>07：西班牙巴塞罗那，圣霍尔迪宫</strong><br /><strong>11：德国科隆朗盛竞技场</strong><br /><strong>14：丹麦哥本哈根皇家竞技场</strong><br /><strong>18：德国柏林，优步竞技场</strong><br /><strong>22：法国巴黎拉德芳斯体育场</strong><br /><strong>25：比利时布鲁塞尔，ING Arena</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> [ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4e2.png" alt="📢" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ] ATEEZ 2024 世界巡演【走向光明：权力意志】北美站<br />⠀ <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f517.png" alt="🔗" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />附加演出公告<a href="https://t.co/037BLMGamH">https://t.co/037BLMGamH</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ATEEZ?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ATEEZ</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%97%90%EC%9D%B4%ED%8B%B0%EC%A6%88?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#에 Beenl티즈</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TowardsTheLight?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TowardsTheLight</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Will_To_Power?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Will_To_Power</a> <a href="https://t.co/Nc6Kry5ujr">pic.twitter.com/Nc6Kry5ujr</a></p><p> — ATEEZ(에기티즈) (@ATEEZofficial) <a href="https://twitter.com/ATEEZofficial/status/1786002709189120121?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> [ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4e2.png" alt="📢" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ] ATEEZ 2025 世界巡演【走向光明：权力意志】欧洲站<br />⠀ <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f517.png" alt="🔗" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />旅游信息<a href="https://t.co/XR6MMoMoGi">https://t.co/XR6MMoMoGi</a><br /> ⠀ <br /><img src="https://s.