0x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/joey-jordison-slipknot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/joey-jordison-slipknot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>创始成员兼鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joey-jordison">乔伊·乔迪森</a>的遗产已经解决了对该乐队从他的死亡中获利的诉讼。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/joey-jordison-slipknot-drummer-obituary-tribute-3004946">Joey Jordison，1975 年至 2021 年：Slipknot 的创始成员，掌握着乐队成功的关键</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候，乔迪森遗产管理公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joey-jordisons-estate-suing-slipknot-for-profiting-off-his-death-3564326">宣布已于去年 6 月对活结乐队提起诉讼，</a>声称该乐队继续在“名为 Knotfest 的活结巡回博物馆”中使用乔迪森的名字和个人物品，并从乔迪森的专用作品中获取利润中饱私囊。尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-82-1238792#:~:text=Slipknot%20drummer%20Joey%20Jordison%20has,exit%20in%20the%20near%20future.">在 2013 年他被乐队解雇后，</a>他们承诺将把他的物品归还给他的家人，但他仍然对粉丝群表示不满。</p><p>现在，根据<a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/joey-jordisons-estate-settles-lawsuit-against-slipknot" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blabbermouth 的</em></a>报道，乔迪森的遗产管理机构已于 9 月 17 日提交了诉讼的无条件和解协议。有关和解的细节尚未公开。 </p><figure id="attachment_3564327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot.jpg" alt="乔伊乔迪森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joey_jordison_slipknot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564327" class="wp-caption-text">乔伊·乔迪森（摄影：Martin Philbey/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>在最初提起的诉讼中，乔迪森的遗产管理委员会还对乔迪森去世后乐队的反应发表了评论：“也许最糟糕的是，克拉汉和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">[科里]泰勒</a>公开向歌迷撒谎，称他们已联系乔迪森的家人，了解他们的情况并表达哀悼和爱意。”乔迪森去世后。这是完全错误的，乔迪森的家人在互联网上读到如此公然的谎言深感不安。很明显，泰勒和克拉汉实际上并不关心乔迪森或他的家人。他们只关心新专辑的宣传和销售。”</p><p>乔迪森 (Jordison) 于 1995 年与已故贝斯手保罗·格雷 (Paul Gray) 和肖恩·“小丑”·克拉汉 (Shawn “Clown” Crahan) 一起创立了这支金属乐队，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-82-1238792#:~:text=Slipknot%20drummer%20Joey%20Jordison%20has,exit%20in%20the%20near%20future.">在 2013 年因个人原因被乐队解雇</a>。乔迪森后来透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-12-1200178">他患有神经系统疾病横贯性脊髓炎</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-founding-drummer-joey-jordison-has-died-at-46-3004210">他于2021年7月去世，享年46岁</a>。</p><p> Slipknot 于 2022 年 9 月发行了他们的第七张也是最新的录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/slipknot-the-end-so-far-review-3317936">“The End, So Far”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3004223" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3004223" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3004223" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2.jpg" alt="乔伊乔迪森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Joey-Jordison-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3004223" class="wp-caption-text"> 2008 年，乔伊·乔迪森 (Joey Jordison) 与活结乐队 (Slipknot) 在伦敦 Hammersmith Apollo 演出。图片来源：Naki/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-weinberg-wouldnt-trade-for-the-world-memories-and-experiences-of-slipknot-3557272">乐队于11月与鼓手杰伊·温伯格分道扬镳</a>，并在社交媒体上分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-departure-of-drummer-jay-weinberg-3531261">一份官方声明</a>，声称他们“有意发展”，并做出了温伯格将离开乐队的“创造性决定”。他的离开是在他加入乐队 10 年后，也就是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-are-seemingly-teasing-a-new-member-3452721">键盘手克雷格·琼斯 (Craig Jones) 在 6 月离开乐队几个月后</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-have-confirmed-the-identity-of-their-new-drummer-3751953">此后，温伯格被前 Sepultura 鼓手埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德 (Eloy Casagrande) 取代</a>，而琼斯则被一位不知名的成员取代。</p><p>这支九人乐队目前正在美国巡演，以庆祝他们的首张同名专辑发行 25 周年。在所有的周年纪念演出中，乐队都恢复了他们的经典造型，带回了红色连身裤和早期面具的元素。他们今年晚些时候也将重返舞台，并计划在英国和欧洲进行巡演，庆祝乐队成立 25 周年 - 您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/slipknot-tickets/artist/763913?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=UM%3AWOmUSgxyPUN%3A1ovyuF3p-UkFSbT3BnWd1180&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处购买门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752482" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752482" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752482" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner.jpg" alt="活结。图片来源：乔纳森·韦纳" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www